'''Miguel Afonso Caetano''' is a young researcher on ''''tactical media'''':

Photo link: http://www.gsd.inesc-id.pt/people/photos/artur_caetano.jpg

Here's his bio:

"a Portugueses M.A. student in Communication, Culture and
Information Technologies at the Higher Studies Institute of Business
and Labour Studies (ISCTE) - www.iscte.pt -, in Lisbon, Portugal who
is writing a thesis about the possibility of existence of an
alternative model of tactical media that goes beyond the adversary
stance, the military and guerrilla language, that doesn't have no
enemies and doesn't depends of that other. He graduated in Social
Communication at the Portuguese Catholic University. Until recently, he
also was a technology journalist, writing for online and offline
Portuguese news outlets."

